ernehmen und zu guter Letzt die Maßnahmen gegen die Piraterie.Im zweiten empirischen Teil werden die getätigten Interviews analysiert und die praktischen Anwendungen erläutert. Gezeigt werden, wie zwei komplett gegensätzliche Unternehmen gegen die Piraterie ankämpfen und versuchen, die Wirtschaftsspionage zu bekämpfen. Daraus erschließt sich ein weiterer empirischer Bereich, welcher die App umfasst. Damit soll eine neue Maßnahme gesetzt werden, wobei Unternehmen und Konsumenten versuchen, in einer gemeinsamen Strategie der Problematik der  9^^a Produkt- und Markenpiraterie entgegenzuwirken.  aeng: Product and brand piracy are problems that have been around for many years now and thus, numerous companies already had or still have to deal with this issues on a daily basis. Besides the companies that are affect, also the consumers and especially those who are buying counterfeit products without knowing it must be more active in counteracting piracy since particularly in the field of technology and medicine, imitations can cause considerable damages to them. Further, the affected companies have to bear the damage, if the consumers believe that they are in possession of an original product and then realize that the quality is poor or that the warranty is denied. As a result, companies might suffer from a severe damage of the public image and also from a loss of sales.The main aim of this thesis is to focus on effects, consequences and safety measures with regard to product and brand piracy. Of particular interest are the measures taken against piracy, not only from a company’s perspective but also from the point of view of the consumer. In this context, the idea of an app will be of major importance since this popular medium could be used as strategy to fight against product and brand piracy.In the theoretical section, the principles of product and brand piracy are discussed in more detail. This includes definitions, different types of piracy, the effects on the consumers as well as on the companies and finally, the measures against the piracy. In the empirical part, the interviews that were conducted beforehand with two companies are analyzed in order to find out about the measures that are taken in practice. It should thereby be shown how two completely different companies fight against piracy and how they counteract industrial espionage. The findings are then used to come up with ideas for the development of an app that could help consumers and companies to develop a strategy for counteracting product and brand  9^^a piracy. 7aHochschulschrift0(DE-588)4113937-92gnd-content  aGraz0(DE-588)4021912-44uvp2gnd2 dHS-MASTER1 aKrickl, Otto3 a2017-075 aUniversität GrazbSozial- und Wirtschaftswissenschaftliche FakultätcInstitut für Organisation und Institutionenökonomik0vls-obvugr-1965157 iAutorIn stimmte der Freigabe des elektronischen Dokuments nicht zu0sF030Aa|1urr|||||170sF050Aa|a|||||||||||0sF051Amu||||||